<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        table, th, td {
            border: 1px solid black;
        }
        th, td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .status-pending {
            color: orange;
        }
        .status-success {
            color: green;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Booking Summary – {{booking.refNo}}</h2>
    <p>Dear {{bookingCustomer.customerName}},</p>
    <p>Thank you for your booking!</p>
    <p>Your booking has been confirmed. You will receive driver contact details shortly.</p>

    <h2>Booking Details</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><td><strong>Trip Reference</strong></td><td>{{tripRef}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Vehicle</strong></td><td>{{vehicleName}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Booking Type</strong></td><td>{{bookingType}}</td></tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Status</strong></td>
            <td class="{{tripStatus == 'Pending' ? 'status-pending' : 'status-success'}}">{{tripStatus}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Booking Rate</strong></td><td>€{{bookingRate}}</td></tr>
    </table>
    <h2>Pickup Details</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><td><strong>Pickup Location</strong></td><td>{{pickupLocation}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Pickup Date</strong></td><td>{{pickupDate}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Pickup Time</strong></td><td>{{pickupTime}}</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Drop Details</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><td><strong>Drop Location</strong></td><td>{{dropLocation}}</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Return Details</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><td><strong>Return Pickup Location</strong></td><td>{{returnPickupLocation}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Return Drop Location</strong></td><td>{{returnDropLocation}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Return Pickup Date</strong></td><td>{{returnPickupDate}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Return Pickup Time</strong></td><td>{{returnPickupTime}}</td></tr>
    </table>

    <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Review your booking details carefully.</li>
        <li>For any modifications, contact our support team.</li>
        <li>Show this email upon arrival for verification.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at +33650500226.</p>
    <p>We look forward to serving you!</p>
    <p>Best Regards,</p>
    <p><strong>Paris Disney Transfer</strong></p>
</body>
</html>